name: Munn - i don't wanna ruin ur party

metadata.description:
When you love someone so much that you'd rather them constantly hurt you in the relationship than just walk away. So, out of love, you let them, because that's how you keep them. 

Thank you for all the love and support on my drops, I won't let you all down, thank you for believing in my music - Munn

Writers: Munn & Dylan Stiles
Producer: Dylan Stiles
